---
import { Phone, Waves, Shield, Eye, Clock } from "@lucide/astro";
---
<section class="pt-2 pb-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mb-6"
      >
        <Waves class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-600" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        ¿Qué es el ultrasonido hepático y vía biliar?
      </h2>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Es un estudio que evalúa en tiempo real el hígado, la vesícula y las
          vías biliares usando ondas sonoras.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div
        class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mb-4"
        >
          <Shield class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sin radiación</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Completamente seguro, no emite radiación ionizante
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mb-4"
        >
          <Eye class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tiempo real</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Observa cómo se comportan las estructuras mientras respiras
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mb-4"
        >
          <Clock class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Detalles útiles</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Información precisa para decidir los siguientes pasos
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/hacer-cita"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-pink-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-pink-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <Phone class="w-5 h-5" />
        Agenda tu Cita
    </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
